title: Ep - 35 - Real World's Las Vegas Steven Hill & Bravo's Amy Phillips
description:
Steven Hill from Real World: Las Vegas explains how he was cast on the show and gives inside scoop on what was not shown on air that season. Sirius Radio’s Amy Phillips reviews with Kate the season premiere of Married at First Sight, which features six people who agree to participate in an extreme experiment: a legal marriage with a complete stranger.
